keyToStrMap.Full:
Cherie the Chef

Occupation:
[] Chef (previously the royal cake tester)

Likes:
[] Thinking of crazy new recipes, eating cake, food fights

Dislikes:
[] Carrots (except in carrot cake!)

Favourite quote:
[] Life is short, eat dessert first!

Favourite people in the (living) world:
[] My mum

How I came to be here:
[] Had one slice of cake too many

What I wish:
[] To taste my mum's homemade apple pie one more time
